  "texts": [
    "This would result in skewed views and an underrepresentation of female authors or authors from the global south.",
    "Furthermore, it could lead to echo chambers in which the most cited articles get proposed more often by GenAI leading to more citations.",
    "Just as with text completion, the paper that is most likely to be mentioned, for example based on the number of citations or the h-index of the authors, does not necessarily give the best answer.",
    "Unfortunately, the best models often cost the most and this creates another layer of implications.When ChatGPT was first launched, it was praised for being open to everyone and celebrated for lowering the barrier of writing in English for non-native speakers [10].",
    "It is a well-known problem that non-native speakers, particularly from the Global South, experience difficulties publishing in English [10]."
